WEBVTT

1
00:00:50.420 --> 00:00:52.660
What's this? Why are
you coming out of there?

2
00:00:53.390 --> 00:00:54.390
I moved in.

3
00:00:55.030 --> 00:00:56.510
I got kicked out of my home.
thanks to a certain someone.

4
00:00:56.590 --> 00:00:57.760
I get that.

5
00:00:58.130 --> 00:01:00.600
but why did you move here?

6
00:01:01.130 --> 00:01:02.900
Aejeong-dong was the cheapest.

7
00:01:03.370 --> 00:01:06.300
The air is nice. and
the view is to die for.

8
00:01:08.870 --> 00:01:10.510
And there's someone
I'd like to kill here too.

9
00:01:14.280 --> 00:01:15.950
Sweetheart. come and eat.

10
00:01:16.920 --> 00:01:18.350
Okay. Grandma.

11
00:01:19.480 --> 00:01:21.390
Hey. get out of the way.

12
00:01:21.950 --> 00:01:24.360
- What?
- I said. move!

13
00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:32.300
Nice landing.

14
00:01:35.370 --> 00:01:37.270
Let's try to get along.

15
00:01:38.370 --> 00:01:39.600
my dear neighbour.

16
00:01:48.510 --> 00:01:50.620
{\an8}It's been a while. Mr. Hwang.

17
00:01:54.590 --> 00:01:57.080
{\an8}You should let me do
things like this. ma'am.

18
00:01:57.160 --> 00:01:58.920
{\an8}- Seriously.
- Why are you eating at my house?

19
00:02:00.190 --> 00:02:03.060
{\an8}I'm anaemic.

20
00:02:03.360 --> 00:02:05.750
{\an8}and I have malnutrition.
which is rare these days.

21
00:02:05.830 --> 00:02:08.300
{\an8}- I'm all skin and bones.
- Oh. you poor thing.

22
00:02:08.870 --> 00:02:11.540
{\an8}- Look at her.
- Just come and sit.

23
00:02:11.840 --> 00:02:14.470
{\an8}Her mother brought seaweed soup too.

24
00:02:14.770 --> 00:02:16.810
{\an8}- Would you like to try some?
- Oh. yes.

25
00:02:23.050 --> 00:02:24.900
- Goodness.
- Oh. my.

26
00:02:24.980 --> 00:02:26.370
This is salty.

27
00:02:26.450 --> 00:02:28.990
Did you scoop this up from
the sea? Why is it so salty?

28
00:02:29.350 --> 00:02:30.640
- That can't be right.
- Unbelievable.

29
00:02:30.720 --> 00:02:33.190
- Have some water.
- To the chef of Hannam-dong?

30
00:02:33.420 --> 00:02:36.930
No wonder you're so skinny. Goodness.

31
00:02:38.060 --> 00:02:41.830
From now on. you'll eat with us.

32
00:02:42.070 --> 00:02:44.940
This is to pay you back for
the watch. So don't worry. okay?

33
00:02:45.440 --> 00:02:48.270
With inflation these days. we're
adding two more mouths to feed?

34
00:02:48.540 --> 00:02:49.860
An office worker's salary only goes so far.

35
00:02:49.940 --> 00:02:52.610
- Do you think money grows on trees?
- Five hundred dollars a month.

36
00:02:53.140 --> 00:02:54.780
I'll pay you for the meals. ma'am.

37
00:02:54.950 --> 00:02:58.980
Please teach me how to cook too.
I'd be honoured to be your student.

38
00:02:59.680 --> 00:03:01.950
Looks like Grandma's got a side gig.

39
00:03:03.760 --> 00:03:05.160
That's wonderful.

40
00:03:06.060 --> 00:03:07.190
I'm not eating!

41
00:03:07.560 --> 00:03:10.230
- Oh. my.
- Adding two more mouths to feed...

42
00:03:10.530 --> 00:03:13.400
What's with his temper?
Why has he changed so much?

43
00:03:14.170 --> 00:03:16.200
- Thank you for the food.
- Go on. eat up.

44
00:03:16.370 --> 00:03:19.340
- Oh. thank you so much. ma'am.
- Sure.

45
00:03:26.380 --> 00:03:27.380
What are you doing?

46
00:03:27.910 --> 00:03:30.300
Thanks to someone. I had to sell my car.

47
00:03:30.380 --> 00:03:32.050
and now I have to walk everywhere.

48
00:03:32.750 --> 00:03:35.290
A responsible society is
a beautiful thing. isn't it?

49
00:03:36.720 --> 00:03:39.520
What? Are you trying to plant
a bug in my car or something?

50
00:03:40.960 --> 00:03:42.160
What are you talking about?

51
00:03:43.030 --> 00:03:45.260
I know you moved here to dig something up.

52
00:03:45.700 --> 00:03:47.100
but that's not going to work on me.

53
00:03:47.400 --> 00:03:49.570
Don't waste your time.
Move out as soon as you can.

54
00:03:49.830 --> 00:03:51.560
What. are you the landlord or something?

55
00:03:51.640 --> 00:03:52.900
Yes. I bought the place.

56
00:03:54.970 --> 00:03:56.470
- When?
- Just now.

57
00:03:57.380 --> 00:03:58.630
Go check with the real estate agency.

58
00:03:58.710 --> 00:03:59.780
then pack your bags and get out.

59
00:04:02.410 --> 00:04:06.350
Hey. that's an abuse of your power.
We have a lease agreement. you know?

60
00:04:06.680 --> 00:04:07.920
Sue me if you have the money.

61
00:04:08.420 --> 00:04:10.290
You have two weeks
until the end of the month.

62
00:04:11.490 --> 00:04:13.160
- Why that little...
- Oh. right.

63
00:04:13.560 --> 00:04:14.760
If you want to catch the subway. run.

64
00:04:18.330 --> 00:04:19.330
Darn it.

65
00:04:31.010 --> 00:04:34.180
It takes over an hour to
get to work? Seriously...

66
00:04:36.750 --> 00:04:37.850
Good morning!

67
00:04:46.160 --> 00:04:47.190
Or not.

68
00:04:48.930 --> 00:04:51.700
Ms. Kang Bang Geul. you don't
seem to have any sense of urgency.

69
00:04:52.760 --> 00:04:56.470
- And you're the last one to arrive.
- You little...

70
00:05:00.240 --> 00:05:03.440
I'll do better.

71
00:05:06.940 --> 00:05:07.980
Where are you going?

72
00:05:12.150 --> 00:05:15.020
I have to get to my desk
now to clock in on time.

73
00:05:15.550 --> 00:05:17.640
The Materials Team's offer for
returns on defective products.

74
00:05:17.720 --> 00:05:19.890
processing complaints for the
Shipping and Customer Service.

75
00:05:20.020 --> 00:05:21.810
collecting bid notices
from construction firms...

76
00:05:21.890 --> 00:05:23.430
and organising material inventory slips.

77
00:05:23.560 --> 00:05:25.600
There's a long list of
support tasks for other teams.

78
00:05:27.530 --> 00:05:28.830
That's your internal work.

79
00:05:30.570 --> 00:05:33.100
You have separate instructions
from the Future Business Team.

80
00:05:35.010 --> 00:05:37.330
You're a new team that
isn't even fully furnished.

81
00:05:37.410 --> 00:05:38.940
You have instructions already.

82
00:05:39.280 --> 00:05:40.850
Team Leader Hwang Jun Hyeon?

83
00:05:47.950 --> 00:05:52.420
Darn. This is all for
show. I'm not strong at all.

84
00:05:52.620 --> 00:05:56.890
- I've had a bad back for ages.
- No whining.

85
00:06:20.420 --> 00:06:21.790
(Choiseong Logistics)

86
00:06:35.530 --> 00:06:36.600
Go!

87
00:06:39.800 --> 00:06:40.840
All right.

88
00:06:46.410 --> 00:06:47.430
(Hwang Jun Hyeon)

89
00:06:47.510 --> 00:06:49.310
Manage the Jungil-dong construction site.

90
00:06:52.150 --> 00:06:54.410
Hey. put your back into
it. Come on. You hear me?

91
00:06:54.490 --> 00:06:55.720
This is solid rock.

92
00:06:56.020 --> 00:06:58.860
(Choiseong Construction.
Jungil-dong Choiseong Town Site)

93
00:07:00.390 --> 00:07:03.190
Hey. you ever handled a shovel before?

94
00:07:03.590 --> 00:07:05.430
No. this is my first time.

95
00:07:05.700 --> 00:07:09.030
But do you think this is deep
enough to bury a person?

96
00:07:21.550 --> 00:07:24.150
Manage the Choiseong
Solution shareholders' meeting.

97
00:07:27.450 --> 00:07:29.120
Please place them nicely.

98
00:07:32.020 --> 00:07:33.590
- Excuse me. coming through.
- Sure.

99
00:07:34.590 --> 00:07:35.630
Gosh!

100
00:07:38.360 --> 00:07:41.000
- Darn.
- You should've been careful.

101
00:07:42.300 --> 00:07:44.220
Gosh. I spent all day delivering packages.

102
00:07:44.300 --> 00:07:47.200
And the next day. I woke up to
calls from nightmare customers.

103
00:07:47.470 --> 00:07:52.300
After getting an earful. I
just apologised and grovelled.

104
00:07:52.380 --> 00:07:53.640
Then I became a master of the copy machine.

105
00:07:54.610 --> 00:07:56.300
You all know what they call us. right?

106
00:07:56.380 --> 00:07:58.320
The Company-wide Task
Resource Management Team.

107
00:07:58.450 --> 00:08:00.080
Or the "Ex-Con Team" for short.

108
00:08:00.380 --> 00:08:02.240
It makes you feel like you've
committed a crime or something.

109
00:08:02.320 --> 00:08:05.790
My heart pounds whenever I hear a siren.

110
00:08:07.260 --> 00:08:10.630
Why is life so hard? Goodness.

111
00:08:12.500 --> 00:08:14.630
I miss my wife and kids in Canada.

112
00:08:18.500 --> 00:08:19.500
This is hard for you too. isn't it?

113
00:08:20.400 --> 00:08:23.610
I'm sure this change of
environment is tough on Ms. Jo too.

114
00:08:24.180 --> 00:08:26.580
How about you just go back to the US?

115
00:08:27.080 --> 00:08:28.130
I can arrange a place for you there...

116
00:08:28.210 --> 00:08:31.580
No. It's not hard at all.

117
00:08:34.220 --> 00:08:35.220
Oh. honestly.

118
00:08:46.900 --> 00:08:47.930
What? What is it now?

119
00:08:52.400 --> 00:08:53.440
Look.

120
00:08:53.670 --> 00:08:55.670
Support work for the
Financial Business Division.

121
00:08:56.040 --> 00:08:59.210
Just thinking about that jerk
gives me a surge of energy.

122
00:09:09.790 --> 00:09:12.090
(Credit Union)

123
00:09:14.090 --> 00:09:16.490
- How can I help you?
- I'd like to withdraw some money.

124
00:09:29.210 --> 00:09:32.240
This lip tint is a bestseller at Sephora.

125
00:09:32.680 --> 00:09:34.480
Number six. Mauve Cherry.

126
00:09:34.650 --> 00:09:36.780
Buy it. and with a quick swipe.

127
00:09:37.050 --> 00:09:38.420
you'll earn cashback right away.

128
00:09:39.780 --> 00:09:43.410
If you use this debit card. you earn
cashback every time you buy coffee.

129
00:09:43.490 --> 00:09:45.420
Can I help you apply for one?

130
00:09:53.760 --> 00:09:56.370
Bang Geul will never give up.

131
00:09:56.830 --> 00:10:00.640
Stop with the nonsense and
pressure her more to quit immediately.

132
00:10:01.840 --> 00:10:04.140
And keep Kang Jae Gyeong away from her.

133
00:10:05.480 --> 00:10:07.470
This will just make things worse
between the father and daughter.

134
00:10:07.550 --> 00:10:08.670
She looks ready to tear him apart...

135
00:10:08.750 --> 00:10:10.180
whenever she hears Hwang Jun Hyeon's name.

136
00:10:11.450 --> 00:10:14.720
Any new developments
with Professor Min Seok Do?

137
00:10:16.350 --> 00:10:17.560
He resigned.

138
00:10:18.620 --> 00:10:20.590
And there are rumours he'll
be joining Choiseong Group.

139
00:10:20.720 --> 00:10:23.130
He might as well be advertising
that he's an accomplice.

140
00:10:25.900 --> 00:10:26.930
Who are you?

141
00:10:28.530 --> 00:10:31.170
Use this video to get some
leverage on Kang Jae Gyeong.

142
00:10:31.870 --> 00:10:33.840
She was the last person to
visit the hospital room that day.

143
00:10:34.000 --> 00:10:35.770
It's not proof that she killed me.

144
00:10:36.410 --> 00:10:37.510
This isn't enough.

145
00:10:38.610 --> 00:10:39.610
What about what I asked you to check?

146
00:10:41.680 --> 00:10:44.620
They said the CCTV stopped
recording due to a security check.

147
00:10:45.150 --> 00:10:47.890
but the person in charge supposedly
mixed up the inspection date.

148
00:10:48.320 --> 00:10:50.120
The hospital didn't
make a big deal out of it.

149
00:10:50.690 --> 00:10:53.360
Jae Gyeong must have pulled
some strings so they wouldn't.

150
00:10:54.230 --> 00:10:55.730
Where is this guy now?

151
00:10:55.830 --> 00:10:56.830
(Personnel Record Card: Ham Du Ho)

152
00:11:01.300 --> 00:11:02.330
Good.

153
00:11:02.670 --> 00:11:04.970
I have no clue.

154
00:11:11.410 --> 00:11:13.680
He's been on sick leave and
hasn't come to work for days.

155
00:11:14.250 --> 00:11:16.350
He asks for a fortune. then disappears.

156
00:11:17.110 --> 00:11:19.680
Find him fast. Before
this gets out of hand.

157
00:11:19.950 --> 00:11:23.890
Yes. We're looking into his
home. family. and all his contacts.

158
00:11:29.030 --> 00:11:31.030
(Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong)

159
00:11:32.030 --> 00:11:35.530
I hear the department heads are
complaining about being overworked.

160
00:11:35.730 --> 00:11:37.430
Aren't you working them a little
too hard. Team Leader Hwang?

161
00:11:37.640 --> 00:11:40.300
Results are most crucial
right after taking office.

162
00:11:40.700 --> 00:11:42.060
Everyone needs to be on their toes.

163
00:11:42.140 --> 00:11:43.130
(Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong)

164
00:11:43.210 --> 00:11:45.980
Also. we heard from Taeha.

165
00:11:46.810 --> 00:11:48.070
They want the Daesan
Hydrogen Complex deal...

166
00:11:48.150 --> 00:11:49.150
wrapped up by next week.

167
00:11:50.610 --> 00:11:52.520
So they just want to take what's theirs?

168
00:11:54.220 --> 00:11:55.550
Secretary Yeo. you can handle that.

169
00:11:56.390 --> 00:11:57.690
(Chairman Kang Jae Gyeong)

170
00:11:57.790 --> 00:11:59.320
Don't you worry about
it. Team Leader Hwang.

171
00:11:59.820 --> 00:12:00.890
Yes. Chairwoman.

172
00:12:07.430 --> 00:12:08.630
(Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong)

173
00:12:09.730 --> 00:12:11.060
(Personnel Record Card: Ham Du Ho)

174
00:12:11.140 --> 00:12:12.170
(Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong)

175
00:12:16.440 --> 00:12:18.040
(Lee Sang Jae)

176
00:12:20.140 --> 00:12:22.580
I think Kang Jae Gyeong is
trying to get to the security guard.

177
00:12:23.080 --> 00:12:25.280
- We have to get to him first...
- I've found him. Chairman.

178
00:12:26.420 --> 00:12:28.690
Do you trust Hwang Jun Hyeon?

179
00:12:30.750 --> 00:12:32.120
Trust him?

180
00:12:33.260 --> 00:12:35.030
He only does things to
stay in my good graces.

181
00:12:36.030 --> 00:12:38.400
Kang Bang Geul moved in next door to me.

182
00:12:38.830 --> 00:12:40.350
I think she's trying to find something out.

183
00:12:40.430 --> 00:12:41.430
What do you want me to do?

184
00:12:41.600 --> 00:12:44.070
I told you I was leaving
the two of them to you.

185
00:12:45.170 --> 00:12:46.240
Handle it.

186
00:12:46.740 --> 00:12:48.340
As I promised. I'll make sure...

187
00:12:49.870 --> 00:12:52.040
the two of them are sent to
the US by the end of the month.

188
00:12:53.980 --> 00:12:55.050
More importantly.

189
00:12:57.350 --> 00:13:00.120
what's making that old man so confident?

190
00:13:09.860 --> 00:13:11.060
Give Taeha a message.

191
00:13:12.560 --> 00:13:15.230
If they don't deliver the money
and shares by the end of the week.

192
00:13:16.700 --> 00:13:20.440
they'll never get their hands on
our core hydrogen technology.

193
00:13:26.210 --> 00:13:27.240
Please.

194
00:13:28.610 --> 00:13:29.750
Darn it.

195
00:13:36.820 --> 00:13:38.390
(Financial Backer)

196
00:13:38.690 --> 00:13:40.820
You have to light a fire under
them before they open their wallets.

197
00:13:41.430 --> 00:13:42.690
(Financial Backer)

198
00:13:43.690 --> 00:13:44.760
Secretary Yeo?

199
00:14:00.610 --> 00:14:03.850
- Darn it!
- Oh. dear.

200
00:14:04.550 --> 00:14:05.820
I'm so sorry.

201
00:14:05.950 --> 00:14:07.790
Do you think saying sorry fixes everything?

202
00:14:08.050 --> 00:14:09.090
I'm sorry.

203
00:14:09.650 --> 00:14:10.750
Unbelievable.

204
00:14:11.420 --> 00:14:14.760
Let me pay for your dry cleaning
and medical bills. Oh. what a mess.

205
00:14:15.630 --> 00:14:18.400
What. you think money can solve everything?

206
00:14:20.500 --> 00:14:22.430
Plus extra for your trouble.

207
00:14:24.470 --> 00:14:26.990
Excuse me! One bowl of ramyeon over here.

208
00:14:27.070 --> 00:14:28.530
and could you please clean this up?

209
00:14:28.610 --> 00:14:30.910
- Thanks.
- My apologies.

210
00:14:31.580 --> 00:14:32.610
Well. then.

211
00:14:36.180 --> 00:14:37.310
Eight. seven.

212
00:14:38.350 --> 00:14:40.280
one. zero. one. two.

213
00:14:42.120 --> 00:14:43.350
(Personnel Record Card)

214
00:14:50.460 --> 00:14:52.060
(Financial Backer)

215
00:14:55.830 --> 00:14:57.050
(Compose New Message)

216
00:14:57.130 --> 00:14:58.140
(Financial Backer)

217
00:14:58.540 --> 00:14:59.570
At 10pm.

218
00:15:00.240 --> 00:15:01.570
The parking lot under Sehwa Bridge.

219
00:15:02.270 --> 00:15:03.270
I want 500.000 dollars.

220
00:15:06.810 --> 00:15:07.980
(Okay)

221
00:15:24.260 --> 00:15:25.330
What's the status?

222
00:15:25.500 --> 00:15:27.500
We've agreed to pay him what he asked for.

223
00:15:27.770 --> 00:15:28.900
so we should wait a little longer.

224
00:15:31.070 --> 00:15:32.470
Still nothing from Taeha?

225
00:15:32.870 --> 00:15:35.810
It seems like they're
intentionally avoiding my calls.

226
00:15:36.210 --> 00:15:37.980
And Secretary Jo is
ignoring my calls altogether.

227
00:15:44.280 --> 00:15:46.280
I wonder what Chairman Na is banking on.

228
00:15:47.820 --> 00:15:49.090
It couldn't be that. could it?

229
00:16:14.680 --> 00:16:15.850
What's he doing here?

230
00:16:20.420 --> 00:16:22.220
(Financial Backer)

231
00:16:27.090 --> 00:16:29.160
Na Byeong Mo. that scum.

232
00:16:37.940 --> 00:16:39.970
- Anyone here?
- No one. sir.

233
00:16:40.370 --> 00:16:42.240
- Head to his house.
- Yes. sir.

234
00:16:52.220 --> 00:16:54.420
(Personnel Record Card. Address)

235
00:17:13.100 --> 00:17:14.740
The security guard disappeared?

236
00:17:15.070 --> 00:17:16.270
We were one step behind.

237
00:17:16.870 --> 00:17:19.710
The place was a mess. Nothing to be found.

238
00:17:20.810 --> 00:17:23.410
How could she team up with
someone like Na Byeong Mo?

239
00:17:24.410 --> 00:17:27.150
She knew full well how much you. hated him.

240
00:17:28.550 --> 00:17:29.590
No.

241
00:17:30.590 --> 00:17:32.360
No matter how I look
at it. this doesn't add up.

242
00:17:33.620 --> 00:17:35.680
Jae Gyeong has no reason
to involve Na Byeong Mo...

243
00:17:35.760 --> 00:17:37.330
in something that could
be used against her.

244
00:17:38.100 --> 00:17:39.100
Then...

245
00:17:42.330 --> 00:17:44.940
Chairman Na is trying to
blackmail Kang Jae Gyeong?

246
00:17:45.870 --> 00:17:47.340
Na Byeong Mo knows.

247
00:17:47.940 --> 00:17:49.540
That Jae Gyeong was the one who killed me.

248
00:17:51.110 --> 00:17:53.640
He was trying to get the CCTV
footage from the security guard.

249
00:17:53.810 --> 00:17:55.780
If Chairman Na gets his hands on it.

250
00:17:56.310 --> 00:17:58.120
he'll obviously use it to
make a deal for Choiseong.

251
00:17:59.020 --> 00:18:00.940
In that case. wouldn't it be better...

252
00:18:01.020 --> 00:18:03.840
if Kang Jae Gyeong's
people got the security guard?

253
00:18:03.920 --> 00:18:06.620
So it's fine for Jae Gyeong to
destroy the evidence of her crime?

254
00:18:10.030 --> 00:18:11.360
There's only one thing left to do.

255
00:18:14.570 --> 00:18:16.320
We have to hope this
has the proof we need...

256
00:18:16.400 --> 00:18:17.670
to prove that Jae Gyeong is the culprit.

257
00:18:18.540 --> 00:18:19.690
(Suspicious Death of Former
Chairman Kang Yong Ho)

258
00:18:19.770 --> 00:18:20.770
(Anonymous Tip)

259
00:18:23.870 --> 00:18:25.780
Hayoung Daily received a tip.

260
00:18:28.280 --> 00:18:29.630
I've stopped them from running the story.

261
00:18:29.710 --> 00:18:31.110
(Kang Yong Ho Died After
Kang Jae Gyeong's Visit)

262
00:18:33.750 --> 00:18:35.090
A tip?

263
00:18:35.450 --> 00:18:37.920
That means we're not the only
ones who suspect Kang Jae Gyeong.

264
00:18:38.660 --> 00:18:40.410
It also means there's
hospital CCTV footage...

265
00:18:40.490 --> 00:18:41.730
from the day of Father's accident.

266
00:18:42.860 --> 00:18:44.730
Proof that Kang Jae
Gyeong is the real killer.

267
00:18:45.400 --> 00:18:47.620
What about the source? Isn't the
paper's president your best friend?

268
00:18:47.700 --> 00:18:49.370
He said he doesn't know.
It was an anonymous tip.

269
00:18:49.630 --> 00:18:52.540
I feel like he's hiding something. though.

270
00:18:54.200 --> 00:18:55.510
You're here. Madam Chairwoman!

271
00:18:57.570 --> 00:18:58.580
(Choiseong C&T. President's Office)

272
00:19:00.740 --> 00:19:03.400
You should have called me.
I'm surprised the Chairwoman...

273
00:19:03.480 --> 00:19:05.120
would trouble herself to come all this way.

274
00:19:07.720 --> 00:19:08.790
You.

275
00:19:10.820 --> 00:19:12.620
Did you meet with the
president of Hayoung Daily?

276
00:19:13.220 --> 00:19:14.560
Hayoung Daily...

277
00:19:15.930 --> 00:19:16.960
You mean Jeong Hak Hui?

278
00:19:17.260 --> 00:19:19.880
I haven't talked to him in a while. Why?

279
00:19:19.960 --> 00:19:21.200
Don't play dumb.

280
00:19:22.170 --> 00:19:23.670
Everyone knows you two are best friends.

281
00:19:25.770 --> 00:19:27.070
Did he say anything to you?

282
00:19:28.840 --> 00:19:31.310
About what? Did an article get published?

283
00:19:33.010 --> 00:19:34.110
Don't tell me...

284
00:19:35.480 --> 00:19:38.820
If you're plotting something with
Kang Bang Geul behind my back.

285
00:19:41.050 --> 00:19:42.590
you'll have to give up your position.

286
00:19:56.870 --> 00:20:00.300
Don't jinx yourself by saying her
name. You have big things to do.

287
00:20:22.390 --> 00:20:23.730
You're getting a call.

288
00:20:24.230 --> 00:20:26.800
Answer it. It seems important.

289
00:20:44.280 --> 00:20:45.570
I was looking for you.
You weren't in your office.

290
00:20:45.650 --> 00:20:48.120
- About Daesan Hydrogen Complex...
- We'll talk later. Mr. Hwang.

291
00:20:54.320 --> 00:20:57.060
I guess they don't let the
traitor in on the important stuff.

292
00:21:01.500 --> 00:21:04.000
She took a call and stormed
out with a foul look on her face.

293
00:21:05.500 --> 00:21:07.870
- Was it about the tip?
- What tip?

294
00:21:08.770 --> 00:21:11.260
I thought you were Kang
Jae Gyeong's favourite.

295
00:21:11.340 --> 00:21:12.710
but you're totally out of the loop.

296
00:21:12.980 --> 00:21:14.810
Tell me what you're talking about.

297
00:21:15.010 --> 00:21:16.970
A newspaper got a tip
that Kang Jae Gyeong...

298
00:21:17.050 --> 00:21:18.550
is the one who killed my dad.

299
00:21:19.520 --> 00:21:21.410
Kang Jae Gyeong's face
was caught clear as day...

300
00:21:21.490 --> 00:21:23.450
on the hospital CCTV that
was supposedly broken.

301
00:21:25.390 --> 00:21:27.190
See? You can't get away with murder.

302
00:21:27.890 --> 00:21:31.430
- The truth always comes out.
- It was Hayoung Daily. wasn't it?

303
00:21:32.630 --> 00:21:34.230
Did you see the article
through Kang Jae Seong?

304
00:21:34.660 --> 00:21:36.400
What exactly was on the CCTV footage?

305
00:21:37.170 --> 00:21:38.520
What picture of Kang Jae Gyeong?

306
00:21:38.600 --> 00:21:40.070
You're not asking the
most important question.

307
00:21:40.800 --> 00:21:43.670
You must know who the informant is.

308
00:21:45.410 --> 00:21:48.110
The proof that Kang Jae
Gyeong killed my dad...

309
00:21:49.550 --> 00:21:51.050
The informant has it. right?

310
00:21:52.820 --> 00:21:53.820
Hey.

311
00:21:55.090 --> 00:21:57.920
Stop running around
playing amateur detective.

312
00:21:59.290 --> 00:22:01.590
There's nothing you can do.

313
00:22:06.500 --> 00:22:07.830
Why that little...

314
00:22:08.500 --> 00:22:09.630
Jae Seong.

315
00:22:10.730 --> 00:22:12.940
It looks like Hwang Jun Hyeon
knows who the informant is. right?

316
00:22:13.640 --> 00:22:15.070
Do you think it's someone we know?

317
00:22:19.780 --> 00:22:22.170
(Choiseong C&T. President's Office)

318
00:22:22.250 --> 00:22:24.210
(Entrance)

319
00:22:48.710 --> 00:22:51.510
Look at this one. It's packed with roe.

320
00:22:52.880 --> 00:22:54.780
It's a delicacy when you eat it whole.

321
00:22:56.050 --> 00:22:57.530
You said you had something to say.

322
00:22:57.610 --> 00:22:59.520
You're always in such a hurry.

323
00:23:04.450 --> 00:23:05.720
(Daesan Hydrogen Complex
and Tech Transfer Agreement)

324
00:23:07.290 --> 00:23:09.030
(Daesan Hydrogen Complex
and Tech Transfer Agreement)

325
00:23:10.730 --> 00:23:13.060
The core technology of the
Daesan Hydrogen Complex.

326
00:23:13.730 --> 00:23:16.870
You'll transfer it without
the final payment. Sign it.

327
00:23:22.070 --> 00:23:23.940
(Daesan Hydrogen Complex
and Tech Transfer Agreement)

328
00:23:25.580 --> 00:23:27.380
I never agreed to a contract like this.

329
00:23:29.480 --> 00:23:31.620
Or will you wash your hands
of Choiseong altogether?

330
00:23:31.880 --> 00:23:35.010
- And I'll graciously let you go.
- Chairman Na!

331
00:23:35.090 --> 00:23:36.370
How dare you raise your voice at me?

332
00:23:36.450 --> 00:23:38.490
You're worse than an animal
for killing your own father.

333
00:23:48.030 --> 00:23:50.820
Place an ad for Taeha
Energy in the Hayoung Daily.

334
00:23:50.900 --> 00:23:53.040
President Jeong does a fine job.

335
00:23:54.200 --> 00:23:55.240
Yes. Chairman.

336
00:23:56.910 --> 00:23:58.010
Was it you?

337
00:23:58.940 --> 00:24:02.910
- You framed me as the killer?
- Frame you? Isn't that the truth?

338
00:24:05.350 --> 00:24:07.480
I should've never gotten
involved with scum like you.

339
00:24:10.350 --> 00:24:11.550
At first.

340
00:24:12.460 --> 00:24:14.420
she was going to drug
Father with the sleeping pills...

341
00:24:14.860 --> 00:24:17.460
she got from Professor Min
so Father wouldn't wake up.

342
00:24:18.360 --> 00:24:20.260
But then Father's eyes suddenly shot open.

343
00:24:20.700 --> 00:24:21.800
so she just grabbed the pillow...

344
00:24:22.830 --> 00:24:25.600
and just smothered him.

345
00:24:26.740 --> 00:24:28.610
So. did he say he did
everything I told him to?

346
00:24:29.570 --> 00:24:30.570
Or...

347
00:24:31.310 --> 00:24:32.880
that he only pretended to go along with it?

348
00:24:33.580 --> 00:24:35.480
Your husband is my accomplice.

349
00:24:36.310 --> 00:24:38.550
You want to see whose crime is worse?

350
00:24:47.690 --> 00:24:49.460
A recording like that
won't hold up as evidence.

351
00:24:50.330 --> 00:24:51.960
Do you really think
people will believe that?

352
00:24:52.160 --> 00:24:54.380
You cremated your father
as if you couldn't wait.

353
00:24:54.460 --> 00:24:56.900
manipulated the board. and
took over as Chairwoman.

354
00:24:57.470 --> 00:24:59.390
Even your family suspects you.

355
00:24:59.470 --> 00:25:01.190
Do you think the public
will believe your side?

356
00:25:01.270 --> 00:25:02.340
Don't slander me.

357
00:25:03.340 --> 00:25:06.210
My father was definitely alive when I left.

358
00:25:09.910 --> 00:25:11.110
Who are you?

359
00:25:16.190 --> 00:25:17.190
Seriously.

360
00:25:18.920 --> 00:25:20.590
You seem to have nine lives.

361
00:25:28.400 --> 00:25:31.170
It wasn't me. I didn't kill him.

362
00:25:32.640 --> 00:25:33.640
Don't tell me...

363
00:25:35.510 --> 00:25:37.170
Did you kill my father?

364
00:25:37.340 --> 00:25:41.540
You didn't care if your father
dropped dead or was murdered.

365
00:25:42.110 --> 00:25:44.310
but you finally look curious now.

366
00:25:47.220 --> 00:25:48.280
Kang Yong Ho...

367
00:25:49.220 --> 00:25:50.910
was murdered by his own
daughter blinded by greed...

368
00:25:50.990 --> 00:25:51.990
for the chairman's seat

369
00:25:52.720 --> 00:25:54.720
I'm going to make that the truth.

370
00:25:56.130 --> 00:25:57.360
What are you. the Almighty?

371
00:25:58.600 --> 00:26:02.530
- How will you hide the truth?
- You can't just hide the truth!

372
00:26:06.000 --> 00:26:07.400
You have to eliminate it.

373
00:26:17.950 --> 00:26:19.920
I heard that guy contacted you too.

374
00:26:20.550 --> 00:26:23.350
He said he'd tell you what really
happened that day for a hefty price.

375
00:26:28.190 --> 00:26:30.590
He shouldn't have pushed his luck.

376
00:26:55.250 --> 00:26:59.120
(Eunpo Sashimi House)

377
00:27:30.890 --> 00:27:33.990
(Kang Jae Gyeong)

378
00:27:36.860 --> 00:27:40.130
(Kang Jae Gyeong)

379
00:27:42.830 --> 00:27:43.970
Yes. ma'am.

380
00:27:46.200 --> 00:27:47.200
Where are you?

381
00:27:59.650 --> 00:28:02.020
(The Late Kang Yong Ho)

382
00:28:10.760 --> 00:28:12.760
Are you hiding something from me?

383
00:28:17.430 --> 00:28:19.870
I came here after reading
the tip sent by Secretary Yeo.

384
00:28:21.070 --> 00:28:22.070
Is it really true?

385
00:28:23.770 --> 00:28:25.510
Did you kill him?

386
00:28:27.380 --> 00:28:28.710
Don't be so cocky.

387
00:28:31.750 --> 00:28:32.880
Did you kill him?

388
00:28:34.720 --> 00:28:36.720
- Your father.
- I said. shut it!

389
00:28:49.430 --> 00:28:51.500
If that's a weakness.
we need to prepare for it.

390
00:28:53.240 --> 00:28:54.240
Answer me.

391
00:28:58.910 --> 00:29:00.180
It was Na Byeong Mo.

392
00:29:01.180 --> 00:29:02.750
He's trying to frame me for it.

393
00:29:04.410 --> 00:29:06.450
I got completely taken in by Chairman Na.

394
00:29:07.550 --> 00:29:09.050
Chairman Na killed him?

395
00:29:11.020 --> 00:29:12.060
Are you sure?

396
00:29:15.830 --> 00:29:18.260
Unbelievable. The whole world suspects me.

397
00:29:19.400 --> 00:29:20.500
Why would I kill my own father?

398
00:29:20.960 --> 00:29:22.200
He was going to die soon anyway.

399
00:29:23.270 --> 00:29:25.340
I already had Choiseong
in my grasp. Why would I?

400
00:29:25.470 --> 00:29:27.770
So you're truly innocent. right?

401
00:29:29.110 --> 00:29:31.470
I am. Not in the slightest.

402
00:29:32.840 --> 00:29:34.780
Then you should request a
police investigation right now.

403
00:29:35.450 --> 00:29:36.450
No.

404
00:29:39.020 --> 00:29:40.950
If this blows up. I'll
be at a disadvantage.

405
00:29:43.520 --> 00:29:44.710
We just need to find proof...

406
00:29:44.790 --> 00:29:46.160
that Chairman Na is the killer.

407
00:29:48.560 --> 00:29:50.060
and then we can instantly
turn the tables on him.

408
00:29:51.830 --> 00:29:53.580
I'll drag Na Byeong Mo to the gutter...

409
00:29:53.660 --> 00:29:55.770
and repay today's humiliation tenfold.

410
00:29:56.000 --> 00:29:57.800
I have to protect Choiseong
and get my revenge.

411
00:29:58.640 --> 00:30:00.640
Isn't that the only way for
my father to rest in peace?

412
00:30:03.710 --> 00:30:05.980
Is that really what your
father would've wanted?

413
00:30:07.480 --> 00:30:08.680
Then what would he have wanted?

414
00:30:11.250 --> 00:30:13.320
If he'd just passed quietly.
none of this would've happened.

415
00:30:14.550 --> 00:30:16.090
So selfish. right to the end.

416
00:30:17.790 --> 00:30:19.360
I'm trying to avenge
him and give him peace.

417
00:30:20.290 --> 00:30:21.320
so what's the problem?

418
00:30:26.330 --> 00:30:28.000
Should I be the one to find it for you?

419
00:30:29.770 --> 00:30:31.830
The evidence that Na
Byeong Mo killed your father.

420
00:30:33.300 --> 00:30:35.570
He already destroyed the
hospital's CCTV footage.

421
00:30:36.510 --> 00:30:37.730
He killed the witness too.

422
00:30:37.810 --> 00:30:39.110
If there's no evidence.
then we'll create it.

423
00:30:40.880 --> 00:30:41.910
I told you.

424
00:30:44.210 --> 00:30:45.880
I'm with you all the way.

425
00:30:48.920 --> 00:30:51.250
What happened between
you and Na Byeong Mo...

426
00:30:54.220 --> 00:30:56.160
Tell me everything.

427
00:31:34.830 --> 00:31:36.620
- You're here. Father.
- Yes.

428
00:31:36.700 --> 00:31:38.700
- This way.
- Okay.

429
00:31:49.050 --> 00:31:50.550
Why is Chairman Na here?

430
00:31:54.020 --> 00:31:55.750
(Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong)

431
00:32:07.160 --> 00:32:10.330
The light in here is amazing. It
makes you want it for yourself.

432
00:32:10.470 --> 00:32:13.900
(Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong)

433
00:32:15.710 --> 00:32:18.170
You still have to sign the
Daesan Hydrogen Complex deal.

434
00:32:19.280 --> 00:32:20.280
Final payment of 100 million dollars.

435
00:32:21.740 --> 00:32:23.580
Settle it according to
the contract. Chairman.

436
00:32:25.480 --> 00:32:28.480
Please. I ask of you.

437
00:32:32.690 --> 00:32:35.930
Should I have played the
recording at the executive meeting?

438
00:32:36.990 --> 00:32:39.500
A lot of people there
still miss Kang Yong Ho.

439
00:32:41.600 --> 00:32:43.200
I'm just kidding.

440
00:32:45.700 --> 00:32:46.700
But...

441
00:32:47.570 --> 00:32:50.110
it wasn't easy for me to get here either.

442
00:32:50.870 --> 00:32:52.380
And I took some major losses along the way.

443
00:32:54.410 --> 00:32:55.980
You'll have to compensate.

444
00:32:56.280 --> 00:32:58.680
You have that secret
stash of money. don't you?

445
00:32:59.850 --> 00:33:01.620
Siren Capital Partners. I believe?

446
00:33:03.720 --> 00:33:05.920
While I'm here. I suppose I'll
have a look around Choiseong.

447
00:33:06.360 --> 00:33:08.090
Don't mind me.

448
00:33:09.430 --> 00:33:10.760
Just carry on with your work.

449
00:33:41.860 --> 00:33:43.160
(Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong)

450
00:33:43.730 --> 00:33:44.880
I've invited you all here today...

451
00:33:44.960 --> 00:33:46.700
as it's a good chance
for us to get acquainted.

452
00:33:47.330 --> 00:33:48.660
In our future with Taeha Group.

453
00:33:49.100 --> 00:33:51.030
there will be many more
projects we can do together.

454
00:33:52.440 --> 00:33:53.740
You'll give them the wrong idea.

455
00:33:53.900 --> 00:33:55.160
(Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong)

456
00:33:55.240 --> 00:33:56.940
I'm the one helping.

457
00:33:57.740 --> 00:34:02.040
Having the title of chairwoman
doesn't solve everything. does it?

458
00:34:02.650 --> 00:34:04.150
And Choiseong has no adults.

459
00:34:07.420 --> 00:34:08.420
President Hyeon.

460
00:34:08.850 --> 00:34:11.190
The automated logistics and
distribution system at Choiseong...

461
00:34:11.920 --> 00:34:13.560
I hear it's running quite well.

462
00:34:13.720 --> 00:34:14.780
(Hyeon Jin. President of Choiseong Distribution)

463
00:34:14.860 --> 00:34:17.260
We're thinking of expanding
into that area as well.

464
00:34:17.990 --> 00:34:19.760
It'd be even better if we did it together.

465
00:34:22.400 --> 00:34:26.100
Are you already in discussions
with Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong?

466
00:34:28.440 --> 00:34:31.410
Why don't we discuss it over a meal?

467
00:34:32.010 --> 00:34:33.380
Taeha will be hosting today.

468
00:34:37.680 --> 00:34:38.680
Chairman Na and his daughter...

469
00:34:39.550 --> 00:34:41.350
even held a luncheon with
the company presidents.

470
00:34:42.820 --> 00:34:44.850
Looks like Na Eun Se is
having the time of her life.

471
00:34:46.220 --> 00:34:47.920
(Daesan Hydrogen Complex
and Tech Transfer Agreement)

472
00:34:50.890 --> 00:34:52.500
If I provoke him without cause.

473
00:34:53.160 --> 00:34:54.860
he might leak the footage
from the hospital room.

474
00:34:56.170 --> 00:34:57.730
Try not to worry so much.

475
00:34:59.400 --> 00:35:02.310
Leverage is only powerful
as long as you hold on to it.

476
00:35:03.070 --> 00:35:04.060
What?

477
00:35:04.140 --> 00:35:06.610
I'm saying Na Byeong Mo
won't play his card just yet.

478
00:35:07.780 --> 00:35:08.780
So.

479
00:35:09.980 --> 00:35:11.280
whatever happens. hold your ground.

480
00:35:12.820 --> 00:35:14.400
It's better than stepping down.

481
00:35:14.480 --> 00:35:15.750
not after all you did to get that position.

482
00:35:15.920 --> 00:35:16.910
Hwang Jun Hyeon.

483
00:35:16.990 --> 00:35:18.810
If you hand over the core
technology without the final payment.

484
00:35:18.890 --> 00:35:20.320
do you think the
shareholders will just stand by?

485
00:35:20.820 --> 00:35:22.210
A chairwoman who gets pushed around...

486
00:35:22.290 --> 00:35:23.830
on her first deal since taking over.

487
00:35:24.260 --> 00:35:26.100
What will the employees think of that?

488
00:35:27.260 --> 00:35:29.900
This directly reflects on your
capabilities as the Chairwoman.

489
00:35:30.700 --> 00:35:33.340
Stop lecturing me and give me a solution.

490
00:35:34.000 --> 00:35:35.000
So what's your plan?

491
00:35:35.200 --> 00:35:37.330
Chairman Na is blackmailing
you with rumours...

492
00:35:37.410 --> 00:35:39.300
and stole the hydrogen technology
without making the final payment.

493
00:35:39.380 --> 00:35:41.580
Isn't that enough to throw a jab?

494
00:35:43.480 --> 00:35:45.850
How do you expect to
manipulate a snake like him?

495
00:35:47.780 --> 00:35:48.950
You have me. don't you?

496
00:35:49.820 --> 00:35:50.820
The icon of betrayal.

497
00:35:53.360 --> 00:35:55.310
You think Chairman Na will trust you?

498
00:35:55.390 --> 00:35:56.660
He either trusts me. or he's dead.

499
00:35:57.890 --> 00:35:59.000
It'll be one or the other.

500
00:36:00.160 --> 00:36:02.470
You won't lose anything either way.

501
00:36:10.910 --> 00:36:11.910
Secretary Yeo.

502
00:36:12.780 --> 00:36:15.010
From now on. follow Team
Leader Hwang's orders.

503
00:36:16.180 --> 00:36:17.850
Give him whatever support he needs.

504
00:36:20.920 --> 00:36:23.520
I'm betting everything on
you. Hwang Jun Hyeon.

505
00:36:34.300 --> 00:36:35.360
Chairman Na Byeong Mo.

506
00:36:37.530 --> 00:36:38.920
This is Hwang Jun Hyeon
from Future Business Team...

507
00:36:39.000 --> 00:36:40.040
at Choiseong Group.

508
00:36:40.840 --> 00:36:41.820
(Friday. March 20. 11:54am)

509
00:36:41.900 --> 00:36:43.310
(Min Seok Do)

510
00:36:48.280 --> 00:36:49.280
No way.

511
00:36:49.780 --> 00:36:51.550
Kang Jae Gyeong is
just letting this happen?

512
00:36:51.810 --> 00:36:53.540
Letting Chairman Na run
wild when he hasn't even paid...

513
00:36:53.620 --> 00:36:54.970
the balance for the hydrogen technology?

514
00:36:55.050 --> 00:36:56.290
It's so strange. right?

515
00:36:56.520 --> 00:36:58.450
He's someone who deserves
to be thrown out on his ear.

516
00:36:58.720 --> 00:36:59.990
But what's even weirder...

517
00:37:00.590 --> 00:37:02.020
is Kang Jae Gyeong's informant.

518
00:37:02.630 --> 00:37:04.760
You found out? Did he share who it was?

519
00:37:05.590 --> 00:37:07.650
At first. the guy swore he wouldn't talk...

520
00:37:07.730 --> 00:37:10.930
even with a knife to his
throat. He played so hard to get.

521
00:37:11.230 --> 00:37:13.700
But two bottles of whiskey later. he caved.

522
00:37:14.100 --> 00:37:16.030
The guy's a lightweight.

523
00:37:16.110 --> 00:37:17.640
But your brother here has an iron liver.

524
00:37:17.870 --> 00:37:19.730
I don't get drunk. I take after our father.

525
00:37:19.810 --> 00:37:21.440
Anyway. the informant...

526
00:37:22.240 --> 00:37:23.480
Who is the informant?

527
00:37:26.680 --> 00:37:28.080
It was someone we know.

528
00:37:29.590 --> 00:37:31.750
- Na Byeong Mo.
- What?

529
00:37:32.660 --> 00:37:35.360
- Chairman Na?
- That viper...

530
00:37:36.030 --> 00:37:38.330
even offered a
multi-million dollar ad deal...

531
00:37:38.660 --> 00:37:40.900
and said absolutely
not to publish the article.

532
00:37:41.430 --> 00:37:45.100
He said to just send the
tip-off to Kang Jae Gyeong.

533
00:37:47.700 --> 00:37:49.490
So Kang Jae Gyeong is being blackmailed...

534
00:37:49.570 --> 00:37:51.710
by Na Byeong Mo over Dad's murder.

535
00:37:54.640 --> 00:37:56.080
Chairman Na...

536
00:37:58.010 --> 00:37:59.280
likes bonsai trees. right?

537
00:38:03.920 --> 00:38:06.920
This is the bonsai expert. I had
a hard time getting her to come.

538
00:38:09.490 --> 00:38:12.230
If the Chairman finds
out. he'll have our heads.

539
00:38:14.960 --> 00:38:15.970
Hazard pay.

540
00:38:17.630 --> 00:38:20.390
- Wait...
- He won't be back for a while.

541
00:38:20.470 --> 00:38:21.500
Don't worry.

542
00:38:29.250 --> 00:38:31.070
Computer hard drives.
external memory drives. USBs...

543
00:38:31.150 --> 00:38:33.070
Find anything that looks
like a storage device.

544
00:38:33.150 --> 00:38:35.170
Okay. Hospital CCTV footage...

545
00:38:35.250 --> 00:38:37.240
or the connection between Kang
Jae Gyeong and Na Byeong Mo.

546
00:38:37.320 --> 00:38:38.720
I swear. I'll find at least one today.

547
00:38:50.630 --> 00:38:51.630
Seok Do.

548
00:38:54.470 --> 00:38:55.470
Mother.

549
00:38:57.240 --> 00:38:59.710
I hear you haven't been home much lately.

550
00:39:01.440 --> 00:39:03.050
I got a call from Il Jun.

551
00:39:04.280 --> 00:39:05.610
He said there was something he was craving.

552
00:39:07.550 --> 00:39:08.750
Don't do this again.

553
00:39:09.450 --> 00:39:10.620
Or just don't answer his calls.

554
00:39:10.990 --> 00:39:12.490
The kids haven't done anything wrong.

555
00:39:12.660 --> 00:39:15.120
Please leave. I'll give it to them.

556
00:39:17.760 --> 00:39:21.430
You did your best to
save your father-in-law.

557
00:39:22.230 --> 00:39:23.970
I know you were sincere.

558
00:39:26.400 --> 00:39:27.400
I...

559
00:39:29.070 --> 00:39:32.010
just want to know the truth of how he died.

560
00:39:34.010 --> 00:39:36.680
For Il Jun's sake. don't do
anything else you'll regret.

561
00:39:38.350 --> 00:39:39.720
You're a father too.

562
00:39:44.850 --> 00:39:45.890
I guess I'll get what's coming to me.

563
00:39:56.300 --> 00:39:58.420
(Multiful 5. Trace Element Injection)

564
00:39:58.500 --> 00:40:00.200
He quit his job at the hospital.

565
00:40:00.970 --> 00:40:02.610
Why would he be carrying
something like that?

566
00:40:27.600 --> 00:40:30.770
There aren't any golf
courses in that direction.

567
00:40:31.600 --> 00:40:33.100
Kang Jae Gyeong. that crazy girl.

568
00:40:36.440 --> 00:40:38.440
(Additional Agreement on Strategic Investment)

569
00:40:38.540 --> 00:40:41.840
That lunatic. Selling our precious
hydrogen business for this nonsense?

570
00:40:43.050 --> 00:40:44.050
Let's just take it.

571
00:40:49.220 --> 00:40:50.520
You're dead meat. Kang Jae Gyeong.

572
00:40:51.220 --> 00:40:53.480
The Chairman is arriving!

573
00:40:53.560 --> 00:40:54.720
In one minute!

574
00:41:30.660 --> 00:41:32.290
I'm a bit late. Chairman.

575
00:41:33.730 --> 00:41:35.500
Welcome. Team Leader Hwang Jun Hyeon.

576
00:41:36.500 --> 00:41:37.500
Let's go inside.

577
00:41:43.810 --> 00:41:45.870
Well. if it isn't the
traitor of the century.

578
00:41:48.810 --> 00:41:50.880
What are you plotting now. Hwang Jun Hyeon?

579
00:41:54.120 --> 00:41:55.640
I thought you might have lost my card.

580
00:41:55.720 --> 00:41:56.950
so I came to see you in person.

581
00:41:57.420 --> 00:42:00.160
When you said you'd serve
me as your third master.

582
00:42:00.860 --> 00:42:02.730
I didn't realise you were being sincere.

583
00:42:03.130 --> 00:42:05.530
The lifeline I'm clinging to
feels like it's about to snap.

584
00:42:05.960 --> 00:42:07.800
They're trying to hush it up.
but rumours are running rampant.

585
00:42:08.730 --> 00:42:10.670
That Kang Jae Gyeong killed her own father.

586
00:42:12.370 --> 00:42:14.040
How is the company in
more of an uproar now...

587
00:42:14.570 --> 00:42:16.270
than when Father passed away?

588
00:42:16.510 --> 00:42:18.730
But we don't know the truth yet. do we?

589
00:42:18.810 --> 00:42:19.880
True or not.

590
00:42:20.840 --> 00:42:23.810
no soldiers will follow a
general who's lost their trust.

591
00:42:24.250 --> 00:42:26.750
Isn't knowing when to
jump ship a skill in itself?

592
00:42:27.750 --> 00:42:30.410
It looks like you've really
got Kang Jae Gyeong...

593
00:42:30.490 --> 00:42:31.820
by the throat. Chairman Na.

594
00:42:40.800 --> 00:42:41.800
Team Leader Hwang.

595
00:42:43.700 --> 00:42:46.170
Do I look like someone
you can just sound out?

596
00:42:52.170 --> 00:42:53.440
That's what Kang Jae Gyeong said.

597
00:42:54.640 --> 00:42:56.610
That you're the one who killed her father.

598
00:42:57.410 --> 00:42:59.230
She said you're framing her.
but she asked me to help...

599
00:42:59.310 --> 00:43:01.250
since she has no evidence
or way to prove her innocence.

600
00:43:01.950 --> 00:43:03.520
It's not that I believe Kang Jae Gyeong.

601
00:43:04.220 --> 00:43:05.220
but why should I?

602
00:43:16.370 --> 00:43:18.200
After everything it
took for me to get here.

603
00:43:18.800 --> 00:43:21.300
She has to pay the
price for trying to kill me.

604
00:43:23.410 --> 00:43:24.610
Your hit-and-run accident...

605
00:43:25.040 --> 00:43:26.610
Was Kang Jae Gyeong behind that?

606
00:43:27.380 --> 00:43:29.140
She's been trading on her
father's name in all sorts of ways.

607
00:43:29.650 --> 00:43:32.680
So. is there any reason I
should help Kang Jae Gyeong?

608
00:43:34.320 --> 00:43:37.790
The one who ruined a promising
young man's life must be punished.

609
00:43:38.450 --> 00:43:40.360
As an adult. how can I turn a blind eye?

610
00:43:41.520 --> 00:43:43.330
Let him go. and then we'll talk.

611
00:43:43.930 --> 00:43:46.360
About how you plan to get your
revenge on Kang Jae Gyeong.

612
00:43:48.530 --> 00:43:49.530
All right. then.

613
00:43:55.740 --> 00:43:57.770
I'll hand over the
hydrogen technology first.

614
00:43:58.840 --> 00:44:00.810
There's a lot more I
can get besides that...

615
00:44:01.480 --> 00:44:02.540
from Kang Jae Gyeong.

616
00:44:16.430 --> 00:44:17.530
I must say. I'm impressed.

617
00:44:18.330 --> 00:44:19.600
Your judgment and
your ability to act quickly.

618
00:44:20.500 --> 00:44:22.360
Now I see why everyone asks
for you. Team Leader Hwang.

619
00:44:22.930 --> 00:44:23.970
You're too kind.

620
00:44:25.930 --> 00:44:26.940
You should be careful.

621
00:44:29.040 --> 00:44:30.070
Thank you.

622
00:44:34.610 --> 00:44:35.680
Are you hurt?

623
00:44:36.110 --> 00:44:37.710
The pain is mostly gone.

624
00:44:38.550 --> 00:44:40.120
but it flares up whenever
I go down the stairs.

625
00:44:50.060 --> 00:44:51.930
(Hangang University Hospital)

626
00:44:52.230 --> 00:44:53.920
Besides Kang Jae Gyeong.
was there really no one else...

627
00:44:54.000 --> 00:44:55.300
who came to the Chairman's room that day?

628
00:44:55.830 --> 00:44:56.830
No. there wasn't.

629
00:44:57.730 --> 00:44:59.540
After Kang Jae Gyeong left.

630
00:44:59.870 --> 00:45:01.770
it wasn't long before that
happened to the Chairman.

631
00:45:03.370 --> 00:45:04.440
Was there anything out of the ordinary?

632
00:45:06.410 --> 00:45:08.040
Please try to think
carefully one more time.

633
00:45:09.010 --> 00:45:10.780
What was unusual?

634
00:45:13.180 --> 00:45:15.320
Oh. right. The stairs.

635
00:45:16.390 --> 00:45:17.390
The stairs?

636
00:45:17.950 --> 00:45:19.220
It was a bit strange.

637
00:45:20.060 --> 00:45:22.890
The elevator wasn't broken. but
she used the emergency stairs.

638
00:45:24.760 --> 00:45:27.480
(Do Not Enter)

639
00:45:27.560 --> 00:45:28.930
(Stairwell)

640
00:45:30.130 --> 00:45:31.630
She took the stairs on purpose.

641
00:45:32.600 --> 00:45:34.370
So she wouldn't run into Kang Jae Gyeong.

642
00:45:35.140 --> 00:45:36.140
Sorry?

643
00:45:36.710 --> 00:45:39.470
There was someone else there that day.

644
00:45:54.860 --> 00:45:56.160
(VIP Ward)

645
00:46:05.400 --> 00:46:07.460
Surely you don't think...

646
00:46:07.540 --> 00:46:09.240
you got to that chair all by yourself?

647
00:46:16.410 --> 00:46:19.480
It was Na Byeong Mo.
He's trying to frame me for it.

648
00:46:22.520 --> 00:46:24.240
They're trying to hush it up.
but rumours are running rampant.

649
00:46:24.320 --> 00:46:26.020
That Kang Jae Gyeong killed her own father.

650
00:46:26.290 --> 00:46:28.660
But we don't know the truth yet. do we?

651
00:46:55.150 --> 00:46:56.150
(VIP Ward)

652
00:47:33.590 --> 00:47:35.790
Someone with a similar
build to Kang Jae Gyeong...

653
00:47:37.490 --> 00:47:39.830
who can easily get things
in Kang Jae Gyeong's style.

654
00:47:41.760 --> 00:47:44.350
Na Byeong Mo's daughter.
who has a deep-seated...

655
00:47:44.430 --> 00:47:45.900
inferiority complex toward Kang Jae Gyeong.

656
00:47:48.700 --> 00:47:49.710
Na Eun Se.

657
00:47:53.980 --> 00:47:55.010
It was you.

658
00:48:00.980 --> 00:48:02.180
You were the one who killed me.

659
00:48:11.260 --> 00:48:13.780
Come on. you should've
gotten a better place.

660
00:48:13.860 --> 00:48:15.600
I'll give you more money. so let's move.

661
00:48:16.000 --> 00:48:18.300
How can an accomplice to a
slush fund move to a nice place?

662
00:48:19.500 --> 00:48:22.340
Jae Gyeong would have me arrested
the second she finds an excuse.

663
00:48:22.500 --> 00:48:24.860
This place is so tiny. There
isn't even room to hide and cry.

664
00:48:24.940 --> 00:48:26.240
How can you live here?

665
00:48:30.250 --> 00:48:31.510
I know you've always found...

666
00:48:33.050 --> 00:48:35.420
a secluded corner to swallow your tears...

667
00:48:36.250 --> 00:48:39.150
like the kitchen. the wine
cellar. and the garage.

668
00:48:39.720 --> 00:48:41.560
Kang Jae Gyeong really tormented you.

669
00:48:41.860 --> 00:48:43.190
You played a part in it too. you know.

670
00:48:46.190 --> 00:48:47.200
I'm sorry.

671
00:48:48.700 --> 00:48:50.030
I wasn't a good person.

672
00:48:50.830 --> 00:48:52.470
I can't believe how immature I was.

673
00:48:56.440 --> 00:48:58.470
Listen to you. acting like
you're all grown up now.

674
00:49:00.680 --> 00:49:03.880
I may be immature. but I'm handy.

675
00:49:06.310 --> 00:49:08.350
See? When I say I'll do something. I do it.

676
00:49:10.520 --> 00:49:12.070
If we leak this. don't you think we can...

677
00:49:12.150 --> 00:49:13.790
keep the hydrogen business from Taeha?

678
00:49:14.060 --> 00:49:16.120
Taeha is the one at a
disadvantage in this secret contract.

679
00:49:16.490 --> 00:49:18.310
Na Byeong Mo won't even bat an eye.

680
00:49:18.390 --> 00:49:20.630
Only Choiseong will be
shaken by the contract scandal.

681
00:49:21.060 --> 00:49:23.230
- But still...
- Jae Seong's right.

682
00:49:23.570 --> 00:49:26.640
And this isn't even proof that
Jae Gyeong is the real culprit.

683
00:49:27.540 --> 00:49:31.640
- Any luck finding that informant?
- Well. about that...

684
00:49:33.240 --> 00:49:34.700
- Darn it.
- My role here...

685
00:49:34.780 --> 00:49:36.000
is to be malnourished. Mom.

686
00:49:36.080 --> 00:49:39.210
- I've got no strength in my hands.
- You really should be more careful.

687
00:49:39.480 --> 00:49:41.620
Let me see if I have some
pants you can change into.

688
00:49:42.650 --> 00:49:43.750
What are you doing?

689
00:49:43.850 --> 00:49:46.420
Don't say anything to
Mom until we know for sure.

690
00:49:47.860 --> 00:49:49.220
What do you take your brother for?

691
00:49:49.460 --> 00:49:50.880
I was going to make something up anyway.

692
00:49:50.960 --> 00:49:52.150
As if.

693
00:49:52.230 --> 00:49:54.980
- You were itching to say something.
- Hide!

694
00:49:55.060 --> 00:49:56.500
- You're just embarrassed.
- I said. hide!

695
00:49:56.600 --> 00:49:58.270
What now?

696
00:50:01.040 --> 00:50:02.670
- What?
- Kang Jae Gyeong's lackey.

697
00:50:12.680 --> 00:50:14.150
That punk.

698
00:50:14.480 --> 00:50:17.150
Where have you been
wandering? You're finally crawling in.

699
00:50:17.520 --> 00:50:19.150
Who did you betray this time?

700
00:50:19.920 --> 00:50:22.740
He must have conspired with Kang
Jae Gyeong to get to Chairman Na.

701
00:50:22.820 --> 00:50:23.880
"Betrayal" is a bit much.

702
00:50:23.960 --> 00:50:25.480
Hey. the first betrayal is the hardest.

703
00:50:25.560 --> 00:50:27.430
The next ones are a
piece of cake. you know?

704
00:50:27.630 --> 00:50:29.730
- Speaking from experience?
- That's it. Why you little...

705
00:50:33.000 --> 00:50:35.440
- Are you okay?
- Gosh. baggy pants.

706
00:50:35.740 --> 00:50:37.540
Totally my style. I love them.

707
00:50:39.170 --> 00:50:40.560
Do you want to bet if Hwang Jun Hyeon...

708
00:50:40.640 --> 00:50:42.300
has switched to Taeha's side?

709
00:50:42.380 --> 00:50:43.410
We'll see who's right.

710
00:50:43.650 --> 00:50:46.050
Why would you make such a childish bet?

711
00:50:48.250 --> 00:50:49.780
We can just find out for ourselves.

712
00:50:58.690 --> 00:51:00.000
You're having bread in
the middle of the night?

713
00:51:00.400 --> 00:51:03.870
Bang Geul just dropped it
off. Do you want to try some?

714
00:51:04.170 --> 00:51:05.170
She was here?

715
00:51:05.400 --> 00:51:06.430
Yes.

716
00:51:21.050 --> 00:51:23.080
(History. No Connected Devices)

717
00:51:24.520 --> 00:51:26.690
Please insert the memory card.

718
00:51:29.590 --> 00:51:31.690
That meticulous jerk.

719
00:51:32.990 --> 00:51:34.000
Grandma.

720
00:51:35.300 --> 00:51:37.630
What do you think?
It's nice and fluffy. right?

721
00:51:38.600 --> 00:51:39.770
I haven't eaten it yet.

722
00:51:40.600 --> 00:51:42.600
It's more delicious with milk.

723
00:51:48.980 --> 00:51:49.980
It is tasty.

724
00:51:50.850 --> 00:51:52.830
Oh. right. Today's trash day.

725
00:51:52.910 --> 00:51:56.150
Oh. I'll take it out. Taking
out the trash is my hobby.

726
00:52:03.630 --> 00:52:04.630
(Unannounced Fire Inspection)

727
00:52:06.560 --> 00:52:08.400
That calculating jerk.

728
00:52:10.230 --> 00:52:12.900
Oh. my. You scared me.

729
00:52:14.100 --> 00:52:16.020
You scared me. Mom.

730
00:52:16.100 --> 00:52:18.070
Aren't you going to make use of me?

731
00:52:22.680 --> 00:52:24.250
What is it now?

732
00:52:24.480 --> 00:52:27.650
I made some savoury pancakes. I
brought them for you. Mr. Hwang.

733
00:52:27.880 --> 00:52:29.070
I don't want any.

734
00:52:29.150 --> 00:52:32.690
How can you say no when
it smells this delicious?

735
00:52:32.920 --> 00:52:35.520
- Come on out.
- Oh. honestly.

736
00:52:35.690 --> 00:52:38.190
You need to eat. You must
be getting hungry by now.

737
00:52:38.660 --> 00:52:41.030
They turned out so delicious.

738
00:52:44.170 --> 00:52:45.170
Right?

739
00:52:49.000 --> 00:52:50.170
(Recycle Bin)

740
00:52:51.040 --> 00:52:52.070
Should I make some more?

741
00:52:52.640 --> 00:52:54.630
- No. that's fine. I'll have that.
- Seriously.

742
00:52:54.710 --> 00:52:57.730
No. Goodness me. Here. have this one too.

743
00:52:57.810 --> 00:52:59.400
- Okay.
- Have this and then eat some more.

744
00:52:59.480 --> 00:53:00.580
I'll take it inside.

745
00:53:00.850 --> 00:53:03.280
Come over here. It won't take long.

746
00:53:03.550 --> 00:53:06.980
- Grandma. I'm back with groceries.
- You've gone to so much trouble.

747
00:53:07.060 --> 00:53:08.990
- Sure.
- Jun Hyeon. give her a hand.

748
00:53:10.430 --> 00:53:11.760
Thank you.

749
00:53:12.930 --> 00:53:14.000
Come in.

750
00:53:27.980 --> 00:53:30.380
Oh. I was just taking a selfie.

751
00:53:32.150 --> 00:53:34.050
Just one quick selfie.

752
00:54:05.010 --> 00:54:07.770
First. replace the laptops
for the Chemical DX Team...

753
00:54:07.850 --> 00:54:09.750
then move on to the
Talent Acquisition Team.

754
00:54:10.020 --> 00:54:11.510
There are departmental
meetings this afternoon.

755
00:54:11.590 --> 00:54:12.620
so provide support for those.

756
00:54:21.400 --> 00:54:22.400
Hey.

757
00:54:23.570 --> 00:54:24.600
What's wrong with you two today?

758
00:54:26.940 --> 00:54:29.460
It seems like Hwang Jun
Hyeon is plotting something.

759
00:54:29.540 --> 00:54:31.210
but we have no way of knowing what it is.

760
00:54:32.040 --> 00:54:34.930
I can't take it anymore. I'm
going to be a man and just...

761
00:54:35.010 --> 00:54:37.800
- No.
- Is this the resignation letter?

762
00:54:37.880 --> 00:54:40.350
Is that the resignation letter
Hwang Jun Hyeon is dying to see?

763
00:54:42.080 --> 00:54:45.270
"To Jun Hyeon. Heart. Hello.
The first time I saw you..."

764
00:54:45.350 --> 00:54:49.280
"They were the things I wouldn't
have done before I met you..."

765
00:54:49.360 --> 00:54:51.390
This letter is meant to
be touching. you know?

766
00:54:52.060 --> 00:54:53.660
I rewrote it more than ten times.

767
00:54:55.730 --> 00:54:58.020
After all we've been through together.

768
00:54:58.100 --> 00:55:00.000
I doubt he's feeling
great about this either.

769
00:55:00.400 --> 00:55:02.870
Jun Hyeon isn't that bad of a guy.

770
00:55:03.910 --> 00:55:08.810
No. he's totally cold-blooded.
He's harsh and just ice-cold.

771
00:55:10.710 --> 00:55:13.210
He's kind of like my dad.

772
00:55:15.550 --> 00:55:16.580
Bang Geul.

773
00:55:17.250 --> 00:55:19.990
The Chairman cared for you a lot.

774
00:55:20.960 --> 00:55:22.190
He just wasn't good at showing it.

775
00:55:22.560 --> 00:55:25.230
It's okay. I don't resent
my dad. He was busy.

776
00:55:25.630 --> 00:55:26.630
That's not true.

777
00:55:27.000 --> 00:55:29.930
When he heard that you
were being bullied in the US.

778
00:55:30.300 --> 00:55:33.150
the Chairman skipped the opening
of the Daesan Hydrogen Complex...

779
00:55:33.230 --> 00:55:34.690
which he'd been looking
forward to for years...

780
00:55:34.770 --> 00:55:37.330
- and flew straight to the US.
- The Chairman did?

781
00:55:37.410 --> 00:55:38.440
Of course.

782
00:55:39.370 --> 00:55:42.010
He tore into them until
they were a crying mess.

783
00:55:42.340 --> 00:55:44.100
He even got a written promise from them...

784
00:55:44.180 --> 00:55:45.550
that they would never bully you again.

785
00:55:45.780 --> 00:55:48.850
But even after that.
he was still so furious.

786
00:55:50.650 --> 00:55:53.290
So that's why their
attitudes suddenly changed.

787
00:55:55.820 --> 00:55:58.460
But why did he leave without seeing
me? He went all the way to the US.

788
00:55:58.730 --> 00:56:00.900
Because if he saw you.
his heart would soften.

789
00:56:01.660 --> 00:56:03.600
and he wouldn't have
been able to leave you there.

790
00:56:04.170 --> 00:56:05.300
But if he brought you back.

791
00:56:05.800 --> 00:56:07.440
you would have had to
deal with Jae Gyeong again.

792
00:56:08.270 --> 00:56:09.570
That's why he held back.

793
00:56:10.000 --> 00:56:12.010
He knew everything she was doing?

794
00:56:13.240 --> 00:56:16.040
The Chairman always felt sorry
that he couldn't do more for you.

795
00:56:17.080 --> 00:56:19.250
He thought that was
how he could protect you.

796
00:56:19.650 --> 00:56:21.280
It wasn't because he didn't love you.

797
00:56:21.850 --> 00:56:24.220
If he was going to die like this anyway.

798
00:56:25.450 --> 00:56:28.460
why did he hide his feelings?
Why didn't he say anything?

799
00:56:30.460 --> 00:56:31.830
He always seemed so larger-than-life.

800
00:56:33.700 --> 00:56:35.760
But the Chairman was
just a father. after all.

801
00:56:35.930 --> 00:56:37.670
Why are you crying now too?

802
00:56:38.570 --> 00:56:41.340
Goodness. Coffee's on me.

803
00:56:41.640 --> 00:56:44.030
- An iced vanilla latte. right?
- An iced vanilla latte.

804
00:56:44.110 --> 00:56:45.110
Just rest here.

805
00:56:45.510 --> 00:56:47.580
Get it from the place
right in front of the office.

806
00:56:48.510 --> 00:56:50.550
Ask them for two pumps of syrup.

807
00:56:57.290 --> 00:56:59.570
- Mom.
- Bang Geul's mom.

808
00:56:59.650 --> 00:57:00.780
If you're done with the bean sprouts.

809
00:57:00.860 --> 00:57:02.040
bring them here so I can blanch.

810
00:57:02.120 --> 00:57:03.390
Yes. coming.

811
00:57:04.660 --> 00:57:07.130
Hwang Jun Hyeon is going
on a business trip today.

812
00:57:07.700 --> 00:57:09.460
A business trip? Where to?

813
00:57:12.100 --> 00:57:14.270
Grandma forgot.

814
00:57:15.040 --> 00:57:16.970
She said it started with Dae-something.

815
00:57:17.640 --> 00:57:19.070
Dae?

816
00:57:19.970 --> 00:57:22.640
Could it be Daesan? You mean
the Daesan Hydrogen Complex?

817
00:57:26.110 --> 00:57:28.150
I told you. you didn't
have to come all this way.

818
00:57:29.580 --> 00:57:31.220
The Chairman doesn't like variables.

819
00:57:31.490 --> 00:57:33.890
Secretary Jo. are you sure
you're not just acting on your own?

820
00:57:37.830 --> 00:57:39.530
Can you really get it out
without the staff knowing?

821
00:57:39.760 --> 00:57:42.700
After I disable the CCTVs.
I'll set off the fire alarm.

822
00:57:43.300 --> 00:57:44.920
The fire trucks will take
five minutes to arrive.

823
00:57:45.000 --> 00:57:46.970
I'll get it out then. so just wait.

824
00:57:47.740 --> 00:57:48.800
Don't worry.

825
00:57:49.740 --> 00:57:51.140
If you're that suspicious.

826
00:57:51.810 --> 00:57:53.010
you can come with me.

827
00:58:08.760 --> 00:58:10.710
- Let's go.
- Fire. There's a fire!

828
00:58:10.790 --> 00:58:12.850
- Evacuate.
- Evacuate.

829
00:58:12.930 --> 00:58:13.930
Fire!

830
00:58:31.380 --> 00:58:32.380
(Enter Password)

831
00:58:37.620 --> 00:58:38.720
(Transferring File)

832
00:58:44.830 --> 00:58:45.860
Why is it doing this again?

833
00:58:46.690 --> 00:58:47.860
But he's dead.

834
00:58:57.410 --> 00:59:00.010
(Lee Sang Jae)

835
00:59:01.340 --> 00:59:05.150
- I'll call you back when...
- Bang Geul is there.

836
00:59:07.480 --> 00:59:11.050
- What?
- Manager Park said Ms. Jo told her.

837
00:59:11.320 --> 00:59:13.820
She seems to know that
you and Taeha made contact.

838
00:59:14.360 --> 00:59:15.960
I think Bang Geul figured something out.

839
00:59:17.230 --> 00:59:18.230
What do you mean?

840
00:59:21.230 --> 00:59:22.460
What are you doing?

841
00:59:24.000 --> 00:59:26.130
- Kang Bang Geul!
- You...

842
00:59:27.870 --> 00:59:29.970
Did you really betray Kang Jae Gyeong?

843
00:59:31.410 --> 00:59:33.010
Did you side with Taeha?

844
00:59:33.440 --> 00:59:35.510
I told you to lay low.

845
00:59:36.140 --> 00:59:37.280
What are you doing here?

846
00:59:45.690 --> 00:59:47.990
What are you doing? Are you crazy?

847
00:59:48.990 --> 00:59:50.760
The rule is to get rid of any witnesses.

848
00:59:51.660 --> 00:59:52.660
Young Lady.

849
00:59:53.800 --> 00:59:56.960
- Wake up. Are you okay?
- Hey. Jun Hyeon.

850
01:00:04.740 --> 01:00:07.880
Darn it. Jun Hyeon. Wait.

851
01:00:08.340 --> 01:00:10.310
Young Lady. are you all right?

852
01:00:10.610 --> 01:00:11.680
Mr. Park.

853
01:00:12.210 --> 01:00:13.850
I'm okay.

854
01:00:25.030 --> 01:00:26.210
- Bang Geul.
- Goodness.

855
01:00:26.290 --> 01:00:27.300
Bang Geul!

856
01:00:30.200 --> 01:00:32.200
Yes. we're at the Daesan Hydrogen Complex.

857
01:00:32.970 --> 01:00:34.470
You should've just gone to the US!

858
01:00:34.800 --> 01:00:36.600
You said you wanted to run
away. so why are you still here?

859
01:00:37.210 --> 01:00:39.470
Why did I never once truly
appreciate this wonderful girl?

860
01:00:40.170 --> 01:00:42.240
The one who would just smile so
brightly when I pushed her away.

861
01:00:43.810 --> 01:00:45.780
Wake up. Bang Geul!

862
01:00:46.180 --> 01:00:48.480
Open your eyes! Can't you hear your dad?

863
01:01:37.430 --> 01:01:38.930
You're still here?

864
01:01:40.370 --> 01:01:41.370
Jae Seong.

865
01:01:59.590 --> 01:02:01.090
This is your last chance.

866
01:02:02.120 --> 01:02:04.230
Make sure my father wakes
up. Your life depends on it.

867
01:02:05.430 --> 01:02:06.430
Yes. sir.

868
01:02:17.410 --> 01:02:18.410
Father.

869
01:02:19.140 --> 01:02:20.140
Hang on...

870
01:02:21.340 --> 01:02:23.040
just a little longer.

871
01:02:29.380 --> 01:02:30.690
Help me!

872
01:02:40.830 --> 01:02:41.960
Is anyone there?

873
01:02:42.460 --> 01:02:45.770
I'm trapped in here. Is anyone there?

874
01:02:46.830 --> 01:02:48.640
I'm trapped in here!

875
01:02:49.200 --> 01:02:50.910
I'm Hwang Jun Hyeon!

876
01:03:02.780 --> 01:03:05.750
(Reborn Rookie)

877
01:03:26.910 --> 01:03:28.530
{\an8}I'm letting you in on my revenge.

878
01:03:28.610 --> 01:03:30.180
{\an8}So from now on. we do everything together.

879
01:03:30.410 --> 01:03:32.400
{\an8}I found the original CCTV
footage from the hospital.

880
01:03:32.480 --> 01:03:35.950
{\an8}Let's show the world what
kind of man Na Byeong Mo is.

881
01:03:36.050 --> 01:03:37.210
{\an8}We've secured circumstantial evidence...

882
01:03:37.290 --> 01:03:38.290
{\an8}pointing to the real culprit.

883
01:03:38.820 --> 01:03:40.680
{\an8}Get all our connections in
the prosecution and the police.

884
01:03:40.760 --> 01:03:42.780
{\an8}If you don't want to be on
the news with Na Byeong Mo.

885
01:03:42.860 --> 01:03:45.190
{\an8}- then throw him in jail now.
- So you're looking for a fight?

886
01:03:45.990 --> 01:03:47.630
{\an8}Do you think my father will
let you get away with this?

887
01:03:48.230 --> 01:03:50.930
{\an8}Get rid of him. And make
sure there's nothing left.

888
01:03:51.270 --> 01:03:54.290
{\an8}You're really something else.
ordering someone to be killed.

889
01:03:54.370 --> 01:03:56.420
{\an8}How about we take over all of Taeha?

890
01:03:56.500 --> 01:03:58.930
{\an8}In that case. may I tell you what I want?

891
01:03:59.010 --> 01:04:01.710
{\an8}My final target is
Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong.
